data_table.description: Food Frequency Questionnaire (FFQ) and Derived Variables, Generation 3 Cohort Exam 1. Variables that have FFQ at the beginning of the description are those questions on the actual FFQ and answered by the participant. Variables that are described as derived fields were calculated using the answers to the FFQ questions. Variables beginning with NUT_ are calculated as 'per day' nutrient values.
